          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protecting Gun Owners in Bankruptcy Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal bankruptcy code to allow an individual debtor to exempt from their bankruptcy estate one or more fierarms, up to a total maximum value of $3,000. The bill also specifies that such firearms are household goods that are not subject to liens in bankruptcy.</p>]]></text>
